full_summary:
### Tender Announcement: Electronic Components

#### Title and Reference
The National Research Council Canada (NRC) is soliciting bids to acquire multiple electronic components under a Supply Arrangement (SA) contract.

#### Tender Details
| **Details** | **Value** |
|iefsOrder   	 _portDiv(E sid Clotharieidentiff.I| Western loud ||
| **Title of Tender** | Acquisition of electronic components | 
| **Solicitation Number** | 24-58081 | 
| **Amendment Number** | 1 |
| **Publication Date** | 2024-07-02 |
| **Tender Closing Date** | 2024-07-16T14:00:00 |
| **Expected Contract Start Date** | 2024-07-30 |
| **Expected Contract End Date** | 2024-10-31 |

#### Method of Procurement
The nature of this tender is competitive and selective in its method of awarding the contract.

#### Solicitation Description
The Construction Research Center (CRC) of the NRC is seeking the procurement of multiple electronic components in order to upgrade its data acquisition system in the laboratory. 

#### Trade Agreements
This tender complies with the Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA) and the Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA).

#### Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this tender, please reach out to Stéphane Lajoie at [stephane.lajoie@nrc-cnrc.gc.ca](mailto:stephane.lajoie@nrc-cnrc.gc.ca) or contact him at (514) 210-7395.

#### Notice and Attachments
The full notice for this tender can be found here: [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/41375/24-58081_npp.noticeofproposedprocurement-avisdeprojetdemarche.apm__0_0.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/41375/24-58081_npp.noticeofproposedprocurement-avisdeprojetdemarche.apm__0_0.pdf)
